attributes.review: This is quite possibly one of the worst apps on the App Store, not just because it was created to support Donald Trump, but because it’s just downright bad! I am not a Trump Supporter, quite the opposite actually (I’m a Bernie Bro). This app is so difficult to navigate and it just doesn’t make sense, if I’m being completely honest. I swear I lost a few brain cells trying to use this app. Even just looking at the icon for the app gives me a RAGING headache. I absolutely, positively, 10000%, do not recommend this app to ANYBODY, not even Trump Supporters! This app is wack as heck and I feel like I need to go back through the entire school system just to regain the brain cells I lost from using it. Anyways, stan Nicki and Bernie 🥰✨🧚
